title: VDOT MDOT DCDOT ESRI, Traffic Counts for Selected Highways/Roads in Virginia, Virginia, 1986-2002
name: VDOT MDOT DCDOT ESRI, Traffic Counts for Selected Highways/Roads in Virginia, Virginia, 1986-2002
description: This is a point file of readings from traffic counter locations from 1986 to 2002 throughout highways and roads in Virginia. The data was compiled from the Virginia Department of Transportation, the Maryland Department of Transportation, the DC Department of Transportation and ESRI.
